/* ───── Cross-Border — North America silhouette (imported) at low
  fill weight so it sits visually beside the filled truck cards.
  Accent still inherits via `currentColor`; corridor strokes use
  `--scene-ink`. Three country waypoints (CA / US / MX) plus a dashed
  route arc. Each waypoint carries an opaque white halo so the pins
  read cleanly over the map shading and the wave wash behind it.

  Coordinates map to the original 1296×864 continent export:
    • Canada pin — populated southern belt, Ontario/Quebec longitude
    • USA pin   — central midwest
    • Mexico pin — central Mexican plateau
  The route arc flows top→bottom in a gentle S, mirroring the
  north–south cross-border corridor rather than a flat east–west
  sweep. */
